'''Mike Edmonds''' (born [[January 13]], [[1940s|1944]]) played an [[Ugnaught]] in the [[Carbon-freezing chamber]] scene in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']]. Producer [[Robert Watts]] liked his performance and promised to keep him in mind for any parts in the next film. In [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], he was cast as the [[Ewok]] [[Logray]] and controlled [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure|Jabba]] the [[Hutt]]'s tail as a puppeteer.<ref name="SW Insider">{{SW|url=news/from-the-pages-of-star-wars-insider-jabba-the-hutt|text=From the Pages of ''Star Wars Insider'': Inside Jabba the Hutt}}</ref>

